esting can be achieved with the proposed model in the\nfrequency domain. The frequency-domain model can achieve the same accuracy yet\n1.548 times faster than the spatial model. This model can also be used directly\non k-space data, and there is no need for image reconstruction.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 13 Dec 2021 17:06:15 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-12-14"}
