 their wave-like capability to interfere and tunnel. Finally, we show\nthat the present approach overcomes the failures of the Peierls-Boltzmann\nformulation for materials with ultralow or glass-like thermal conductivity.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 13 Dec 2021 18:53:55 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Sun, 10 Jul 2022 15:04:48 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-07-12"}
