bserved in FRBs\ncould be due to scattering in a warm magnetar wind.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 13 Dec 2021 21:13:20 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 26 Jan 2022 04:00:32 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-02-09"}
