ntested and commissioned with cosmic rays. The author will describe the detector\ndesign, the quality assurance and certification path, as well as will present\nthe experience with the chamber tests, the integration procedure and\ninstallation of the muon stations in the ATLAS experiment.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 13 Dec 2021 21:25:36 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-12-15"}
