 for the equation of state larger (or smaller) than\n1/3 hence $N_{re}\\neq0$. The maximum temperature at the end of reheating is\n$T_{re}^\\text{max}\\simeq3\\times 10^{15}$ GeV, which corresponds to the\ninstantaneous reheating. The low reheating temperature, as low as a few MeV, is\nalso possible when $\\omega_{re}$ is closer to $1/3$.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 14 Dec 2021 07:25:11 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-04-13"}
