 thickness - from 0 mm (converter is absent) to\n8 mm with a step of 1 mm. The developed program operates in a multithreaded\nmode. The G4EmStandardPhysics_option3 model of the PhysicsList was used in the\ncalculations. A detailed analysis of the obtained data has been performed. As a\nresult of the data analysis, the optimal value of the tungsten converter\nthickness was obtained.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 14 Dec 2021 14:52:40 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-12-15"}
