ent is conducted on the subset of the\nlatest CICIDS2017 network dataset. The overall accuracy and AUC of SHAP_Model\nis 94% and 0.969, respectively.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 14 Dec 2021 09:42:04 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-12-17"}
